A 40-year-old famous Soweto-born rapper has been arrested and charged with the murder of his wife. It’s understood that the rapper’s 41-year old wife was initially thought to have died of natural causes. She was was found dead in a room on the 31st of December. However, police suspected foul play and have opened a murder docket. Police spokesperson Lungelo Dlamini says the suspect will appear in the Hillbrow Magistrate’s Court on Thursday.